# Simply LaRae — Environment Configuration
#
# SITE MODE
# Controls the public homepage.
#
# "coming_soon" → Shows the launch/partnership page (default while pre-launch)
# "full"        → Restores the complete Simply LaRae website
#
# To restore the full site: change the value below to "full" and restart the dev server.
VITE_SITE_MODE=coming_soon
